  <h2 class="section-title">The Pattern</h2>

  <p>
    The Calendar Tetris Master believes that a full calendar equals a productive
    day. Every slot is filled. Meetings start back-to-back. There's no time for
    focused work, bathroom breaks, or processing what was discussed. The
    calendar is a game of Tetris, and every gap must be filled.
  </p>

  <p>
    For knowledge workers â€” developers, designers, writers, strategists â€” this
